OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of clear intervals and
OL,7,Fshowers, these more frequent over
OL,8,FPerthshire and the Trossachs in the
OL,9,Fevening and early night. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fotherwise rather cloudy. Mainly dry
OL,13,Fwith just a few scattered showers.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,16,Fon Saturday with showers or perhaps
OL,17,Fsome longer spells of rain. Dry much
OL,18,Fof Sunday then rain spreading from
OL,19,Fnorthwest, lasting into Monday before
OL,20,Fbrightening up later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
